  "reference_number": "RUS1358",
  "remarks": "\n GTLK JSC is a Russian leasing company focused on, air, railway, and water transportation. They are a state-owned company directly controlled by the Government of the Russian Federation. GTLK JSC therefore obtains a benefit from the Government of Russia by being a Government of Russia-affiliated entity, and are therefore considered to be an involved person.  \n The trust services sanctions were imposed on 21/03/2023.",
